Gradebook Management System (Excel)

1. Project Overview
This Excel project is designed to manage and evaluate student scores efficiently. It automates calculations and helps determine pass/fail status using Excel formulas.

2. Features
- Score recording and management
- Automatic percentage calculation
- Pass/Fail evaluation
- Logical functions implementation
- User-friendly spreadsheet layout

3. Skills Used
- Microsoft Excel
- Formulas and Functions
- Logical Functions (OR)
- Data Analysis
- Spreadsheet Management

4. Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel

5.Objective
To automate grade calculations and reduce manual effort while improving accuracy in student performance evaluation.
